dataIdInfo.idPurp: Administrative boundary lines for admin level 0-2. An 'AdminLevel' field is used to attribute the lines. The values used for this field are 0,1,2,99. 0 is international border, 99 is coastline, 1 is Admin1 border, 2 is Admin2 border. Each line is attributed with the highest admin level that it can participate in.
